Package: hypotheticalTreatmentAccelerations
Title: Hypothetical Treatment Accelerations
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Haris", "Fawad", , "haris.fawad@medisin.uio.no", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1885-5846"))
Description: An implementation of the hypothetical treatment accelerations described in https://arxiv.org/abs/2207.07893.
    This package includes a simulated data set, on which a user can specify a treatment acceleration and plot the resulting estimate of the survival function.
